<plot>Death is an event that happens to everyone and there has always been a question about what happens in the afterlife. This is the story of what occurs between life and death. A group of deceased young people are waiting their turn to move on to the next life, whatever that may be. Most aren't worried about what will happen, but there's one teenager who is beginning to wonder if the mistakes of his life will ruin his afterlife. Can his sole confidant give him any hope?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?394750</url></doc>
